      <title>拉胡尔·甘地将争夺印度北方邦关键席位的民意调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/rahul-gandhi-to-contest-key-seat-in-uttar-pradesh-in-india-polls</link>
